description: Well my PAPIs...here it is. I told you guys I was going to bring you more of my PAPI brand of fun. This night we come to you from club Twist. We had such a super time. Sebastian...wearing the pink shirt...was such a PAPI. I had my eye on him the whole night. Rayos que hombre. At the end of night he was with us giving me some private time. I love my job.
title: Twist And Shout
